msgid "plugins.generic.issueSpotlight.settings.apiKey"
msgstr "Gemini API Key"

msgid "plugins.generic.issueSpotlight.settings.apiKeyDescription"
msgstr "In order for the plugin to work, an access key for Google's artificial intelligence (Gemini) is required. This key enables the automatic analysis of titles and abstracts to generate the editorial, radar, SDGs, and institutional map.<br><br><strong>Consumption and Limits:</strong> Each complete issue analysis makes 4 calls to the Gemini LLM. The Gemini free plan allows a maximum of 20 daily requests.<br><br><strong>How to obtain the key:</strong><br>1. Go to <a href=\"https://aistudio.google.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Google AI Studio</a>.<br>2. Click on 'Get API key'.<br>3. Click on 'Create API key'.<br>4. Copy the key (it has a format similar to: <code>AIzaSyC3xY9mN2pQ7rT8vU1wX4zK6jL5hM9nO0p</code>) and paste it here.<br><br><strong>How to run the analysis:</strong><br>Once the key is configured, go to <strong>Issues</strong> in the backend, click on the dropdown arrow for the issue you want to analyze and select the <strong>IssueSpotlight IA</strong> link to run the intelligent analysis."

